but contacting the dead is a superstition too far.

3
00:14:52.360 --> 00:14:54.940 
我... 我不喜欢"死人"这个词
Oh, I... I... I don't like the term "dead".

4
00:14:56.800 --> 00:14:59.030 
你总是持怀疑态度的啊 姨妈
You're usually so sceptical, Aunt.

5
00:14:59.080 --> 00:15:02.380 
因为我越来越老 离我的...
Well, as I get older and closer to my...

6
00:15:02.380 --> 00:15:03.550 
离开
Departure.

7
00:15:04.680 --> 00:15:08.510 
离开越来越近... 我变得开明了很多
Departure... I become more open-minded.

8
00:15:09.360 --> 00:15:13.150 
我也会治好马戈的青春痘 用我的信念疗法
I'll also cure Margo's spots, using my faith healing.

9
00:15:13.710 --> 00:15:15.870 
恐怕我得继续工作了
I'm afraid I must resume my work.

10
00:15:15.920 --> 00:15:17.490 
我在写一篇论文
I'm giving a paper about

11
00:15:17.520 --> 00:15:19.030 
是关于头足类动物和它们的墨囊
cephalopods and their inky sacs.

